      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained driver that has been treated with care. The exterior finish maintains a high gloss, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical signs of careful use that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is soft and intact, showing only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Every feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium audio system and navigation, is in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a complete service history with the most recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine idles smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. The tires are matching sets with deep tread remaining, ensuring you won't need an upgrade anytime soon. I am including all original manuals and two sets of keys. This is a solid, honest car that performs beautifully on both city streets and long highway hauls.",
